{
  "stem": "5313.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was about, I don't know, a 10-inch hole I saw there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I happened to know that when we walked in, it was water near that building.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And with my new shoes, you know, I knocked a little hole as big as that I could get out of that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I jumped into the water, you know, much as I could.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a lot of ship was, at that time, bombed over there, you know, ruined ship.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was there all night, 'til in the morning, you know, they was pushing again us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They was putting everybody close to the water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I swim back again to mine people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's the way I saved my life at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, let me explain.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Yugoslav people, they begged us to run away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're hiding us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They put food, you know, along the highway, what they was risking their own life, you know, to-- some German would see that they're putting food there, you know, they would kill them too.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's the way you were treated, you know, along the way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we hit further to the Muslim section of Yugoslavia, we was treated again very bad, I can tell you that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Respect that I wanted incident outright to hide.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I thought, you know, I'm still in-- in Yugoslavia, which was supposed to be Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was running away with another friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we hided-- you know, I don't know how they call that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, in Europe they was putting corn away for the winter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Silo.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we was hiding there, you know, during the night.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
